name: Cube Skater
description:
You control a cube and you have to move to dodge obstacles coming your way. Use A and D or the arrow keys to move left and right. There are 10 levels which get progressively harder. Good Luck! (You'll need it)

Version 1.2
- Fixed wacky collision in level 10

Version 1.1
- Added level counter
- Removed score counter
- Title changed to Cube Skater

Version 1.0
- Cube Runner launched
